Package: USQ.xaringan
Title: Xaringan Template With Univerity of Southern Queensland Corporate Identity
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Adam H.",
           family = "Sparks",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "adamhsparks@usq.edu.au")
Description: A template and CSS files for reproducing the corporate identity
    presentation style of the University of Southern Queensland `xaringan`.
    USQ's templates are available internally as Powerpoint Slide Templates only.
    This package lets you achieve that style while also being able to take
    advantage of RMarkdown. Please note that this package is not an official
    product of USQ.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/adamhsparks/usq_xaringan
